body.content:
Hello,
I came across your email address through the google sites and I have a
great feeling over it. Apologies for my surprising email to you.I want to
chat with you. My age is 23 years old . I am an interesting and kind girl.
I can write that I am a romantic person. I dream of finding a decent person
with whom I can share a wonderful panpal life! I am looking for a reliable
person to share our feelings as brother or sister from another mother. If
you might think we are suitable for each other, I look forward to hearing
from you. Friendship doesn't think about distance,age or color. Friendship
is hearing each other's voice from the heart. A friend is a gift of love
from God and someone who cares as much as you do. I'm Miss Favour,I want to
be your friend. I'll be glad to read from you and I will reply with my
picture as we get to know better.
Best regards
Miss Favour.
